title: HOUR 1- Rick Neuheisel 081220
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Rick Neuheisel 081220
description:
Rick Nueheisel tells Dan that the thing that has stood out to him is the discord that is going on in the Big 10 right now with teams like Nebraska wanting to go to other conferences to play this fall. Rick says Coaches just want to save their programs; and if he were a coach right now in a non-playing conference; the main thing he would be doing is trying to save players from transferring.
